{"tid":410230,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港應否恢復死刑？","createTime":"2017-09-22T17:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T16:43:55.000Z","uid":61,"like":38,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa7caa52262543d8da0d155ec4a52b85ddff5e8","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"停止執行<br />\n雖然香港於1966年11月16日後停止執行死刑，但1966年至1993年的香港法例中仍然保存死刑，而法庭亦會依據法例，判處犯人環首死刑。不過所有在當時被判刑的死囚，都會一律自動由英女王伊利莎白二世或港督赦免，改為終身監禁（自香港開埠初期起，《皇室訓令》即已賦予港督自行決定是否赦免死刑的權力，毋須先獲得英國政府批准）。<br />\n香港自從停止執行死刑後，暴力罪行日益猖獗，殺人案由1966年前每年不足30宗，急增至1972年115宗，此時港府正要展開撲滅暴力罪行運動。<br />\n1973年，發生死囚蔡國昌免死爭議事件：在1972年1月26日凌晨，無業青年蔡國昌與兩名男子，打劫元朗洪水橋一間士多店，刺死任職輔警的東主兒子，及劫去170元；同年11月，蔡被判謀殺及打劫罪成，判處繯首死刑。1973年4月，時任港督麥理浩宣布考慮行政局建議後，決定不對蔡赦免死刑，為自1966年11月16日最後一次執行死刑後，近6.5年以來首次不赦免死囚死刑。民間苦於停止執行死刑後暴力罪行急增，普遍支持港督決定。<br />\n隨後，香港宗教領袖徐誠斌、白約翰、及一些御用大律師等71人，聯名上書英國聯邦事務部大臣（英國外相）及下議院反對黨領袖，求免蔡死刑，他們指出自1966年11月16日後，至當時約6.5年間，一直沒有執行死刑，且已赦免了30名死囚死刑，政府已予民間不再執行死刑的印象，在事前沒有宣布不再赦免下，赦免了30名死囚後卻忽然不赦免這第31名，對蔡並不公平。1973年5月15日，英女王接受聯邦事務部大臣的建議，赦免蔡的死刑，改為終身監禁。民間對此大感失望憤慨，強烈抨擊英國政府恣意干涉香港事務，不理會香港實際情況，並且違背香港絕大多數的民意。香港天主教徒也指責徐主教參加聯署，以致教會需公開澄清，認為政府為大眾的利益，有權及有義務執行合法的死刑。<br />\n1975年11月6日，輔政司（Colonial Secretary）羅弼時在立法局會議上宣布，香港不會恢復執行死刑，主要因為英國政府阻撓。他稱港督麥理浩多次要求英國政府，准許香港恢復死刑，以收阻嚇作用，但都不獲允准。他又指出英女王會徵求外相意見，決定是否赦免死刑，而外相又要考慮英國國會的反應，如建議香港執行死刑，會遭到下議院的反對。1974年羅德丞獲委任為立法局議員後，已大力批評英國拒絕香港執行死刑，將最後決定權從港督手上奪去，相信大臣向英女王建議免除死刑，純粹是出於政治動機，又因香港市民不能參與英國國會選舉，即使香港民意普遍支持死刑，也不會影響到英國政府。在香港司法部門服務近三十年的百里渠也認為，一個自由社會的法律和司法機構，應該反映人民的一般意見和觀點，不是理想主義者或思想古怪人士的看法，因此香港居民主張維持死刑，這意願應予尊重，並且指出當法律明文規定了死刑卻不執行，會導致不滿。他也同意死刑對潛存的殺人者有嚇阻作用。<br />\n廢除<br />\n香港政府於1991年6月提交草案立法廢除死刑，曾經引起社會的討論。1992年，有一個名為香港民眾聯會的組織宣稱其民意調查結果，約有七成香港市民不支持廢除死刑，而香港律師會及香港大律師公會則同意廢除死刑。立法局於1993年4月三讀通過修訂法例，以終身監禁作為最高刑罰，正式廢除死刑。<br />\n<br />\n如果因為提早釋放而唔需要坐成世，咁判刑個意義可在？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持恢復死刑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔需要，俾次機會"},{"pid":"c2f313a0abff5f93dda07cafe01c7a8808c0e727","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"利申返，我絕對覺得香港有死刑需要"},{"pid":"b73aa4ddca8006396e60536d0f659ab20f4ac0f9","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"def03c6b7b19d6d15d79519e7235dbb88324ea2f","tid":410230,"uid":138613,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得要<br />\n不過如果畀佢拎嚟對付政治犯就大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f731147162e96f08d70404d2a911ec503515ec","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"我認為恢復死刑只係用於判決謀殺罪上邊，其他一律不適用"},{"pid":"f32e2a6bff90f00fcbc7681dfef91e6a1f29db2b","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c8de531bc7bc38dedbaa3892ccb0fcd245f994a","tid":410230,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"建國後民建聯班賤種一定要上斷頭台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5097abd37421a6e36e59c85db07516e7df20b1c8","tid":410230,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"殺人塡命，天公地道"},{"pid":"05b74c412b864f789f32249709c79e17da8338b1","tid":410230,"uid":37393,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"依家香港司法制度咁樣，有死刑只會比當權者用黎做合法殺人既手段"},{"pid":"d5e5b7f1abb278fcd4e0078701f4ac7d70a55b1b","tid":410230,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:01:29.000Z","msg":"應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拉鳩晒搭地鐵衝閘班撚樣去打靶咁啱"},{"pid":"0b5aae9c2417de1435934888b845225f99ce23a9","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家香港司法制度咁樣，有死刑只會比當權者用黎做合法殺人既手段</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都話恢復只係用作裁決謀殺罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為謀殺根本唔應該只判終身監禁咁簡單，佢仲有可能提早釋放，唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7bc7b1e82a42164eb13266b6e8cab444b41404","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建國後民建聯班賤種一定要上斷頭台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然無殺人，但我都好希望佢地上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96031c067292a7acec1aa59670680647304cafcd","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺人塡命，天公地道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，絕對同意"},{"pid":"8c380350951bf326ecb8cd5492b6f0e6825d26fc","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拉鳩晒搭地鐵衝閘班撚樣去打靶咁啱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阻住上車廢老都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b90f2d84f806457b55790add186dd7dc50ccf7","tid":410230,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"終身折磨先有用<br />\n有D撚樣死係太便宜佢"},{"pid":"f38f1ea1b20d587922e34242fda14ad3597c312e","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終身折磨先有用<br />\n有D撚樣死係太便宜佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題好多都提早釋放，好唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e8df050da64788d43c181322bb26d9af1a8339","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"扮嘢扮到好有誠意改，有悔意就有可能放返出黎，出到黎適應唔到，犯多次事算數，到時一個社會炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b647f533046e0f505c1694b56304c24a4b3354d2","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T19:18:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97fd59aa877612f7c1756a39e9f7c52f803d7000","tid":410230,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T19:45:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d21eb9401325e10882ec365335eb670565f067c1","tid":410230,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:06:39.000Z","msg":"大王都就出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fbb00a1edb0c90dd51034464078f545f1b0cd0","tid":410230,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大王都就出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />viu應該搵佢做訪問"},{"pid":"489a3449369995acf8cc47e8a7304d67c7185e43","tid":410230,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"支持暴動罪全部判死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e780c3409d666c23b1dea0bae75dccec61211acd","tid":410230,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 梗係要<br />\n捉班囤地死賤種打靶"},{"pid":"3704ec8af1ad58215b32817c6087d05043db3c75","tid":410230,"uid":133036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"首先，以香港現有情況。<br />\n如果真係恢複死刑，港共政權一定會令好多思想獨立，擁有自由志嘅人死9曬；<br />\n而應要接受死刑果d，好似7惡呀~賣港賊果班，佢哋依傢會踩住香港人嘅屍骸安享太平。<br />\n<br />\n所以以現時來講，我反對。"},{"pid":"5de167856c3d88f70587a73df9c01a5175431e01","tid":410230,"uid":133036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家香港司法制度咁樣，有死刑只會比當權者用黎做合法殺人既手段</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都話恢復只係用作裁決謀殺罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為謀殺根本唔應該只判終身監禁咁簡單，佢仲有可能提早釋放，唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港共政權有咩做唔出，你睇果單usb線自殺案？<br />\n到時大把唔知係唔係真係殺咗人嘅案出現；<br />\n然後成班無辜嘅死刑，一句集體謀殺，又可以一次判死十幾件。"}]}